• Footprinting Countermeasures 

Organizations should reduce information exposure.

Countermeasures :-
1. Hide sensitive documents.
2. Remove metadata from files.
3. Use privacy-protected registration where appropriate.
4. Limit employee information exposure.
5. Secure DNS infrastructure.
6. Implement security headers.
7. Conduct security awareness training.

